{"prompt": "Build a user-friendly site for a local animal adoption center. The design should prominently display a gentle cornflower blue.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Pawsitive Connections Animal Shelter</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #f0f8ff; /* A very light, subtle off-white */\n            color: #333;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        header {\n            background-color: #6495ed; /* Cornflower blue */\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n        }\n        nav {\n            text-align: center;\n            margin: 20px 0;\n        }\n        nav a {\n            color: #6495ed; /* Cornflower blue */\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: #4682b4; /* Steel blue for hover */\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n        section {\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 30px;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);\n        }\n        h2 {\n            color: #4682b4; /* Steel blue */\n            border-bottom: 2px solid #6495ed; /* Cornflower blue underline */\n            padding-bottom: 10px;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n        .animal-gallery {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));\n            gap: 20px;\n        }\n        .animal-card {\n            border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            background-color: #f9f9f9;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .animal-card:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        .animal-card img {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 200px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n            display: block;\n        }\n        .animal-info {\n            padding: 15px;\n        }\n        .animal-info h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            color: #6495ed; /* Cornflower blue */\n        }\n        .animal-info p {\n            margin-bottom: 5px;\n        }\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: #6495ed; /* Cornflower blue */\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 10px 20px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            margin-top: 15px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: #4682b4; /* Steel blue */\n        }\n        footer {\n            background-color: #6495ed; /* Cornflower blue */\n            color: #ffffff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n        }\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <h1>Pawsitive Connections Animal Shelter</h1>\n        <p>Giving every animal a second chance.</p>\n    </header>\n    <nav>\n        <a href=\"#about\">About Us</a>\n        <a href=\"#adopt\">Adoptable Animals</a>\n        <a href=\"#volunteer\">Volunteer</a>\n        <a href=\"#donate\">Donate</a>\n    </nav>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section id=\"about\">\n            <h2>Welcome to Pawsitive Connections</h2>\n            <p>We are a dedicated team committed to rescuing, rehabilitating, and rehoming animals in need. Our mission is to create loving, forever homes for every pet that comes through our doors. We believe that every animal deserves a safe and caring environment.</p>\n        </section>\n        <section id=\"adopt\">\n            <h2>Meet Our Adoptable Friends</h2>\n            <div class=\"animal-gallery\">\n                <div class=\"animal-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/250x200/cccccc/ffffff?text=Buddy+the+Dog\" alt=\"Buddy the Dog\">\n                    <div class=\"animal-info\">\n                        <h3>Buddy</h3>\n                        <p><strong>Breed:</strong> Golden Retriever Mix</p>\n                        <p><strong>Age:</strong> 3 years</p>\n                        <p><strong>Gender:</strong> Male</p>\n                        <p>Buddy is a playful and affectionate dog who loves long walks and cuddles. He's great with kids and other dogs.</p>\n                        <a href=\"#\" class=\"cta-button\">Learn More & Adopt</a>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"animal-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/250x200/cccccc/ffffff?text=Luna+the+Cat\" alt=\"Luna the Cat\">\n                    <div class=\"animal-info\">\n                        <h3>Luna</h3>\n                        <p><strong>Breed:</strong> Domestic Shorthair</p>\n                        <p><strong>Age:</strong> 2 years</p>\n                        <p><strong>Gender:</strong> Female</p>\n                        <p>Luna is a sweet and curious cat who enjoys sunbathing and chasing toy mice. She's a bit shy at first but warms up quickly.</p>\n                        <a href=\"#\" class=\"cta-button\">Learn More & Adopt</a>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"animal-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/250x200/cccccc/ffffff?text=Rocky+the+Rabbit\" alt=\"Rocky the Rabbit\">\n                    <div class=\"animal-info\">\n                        <h3>Rocky</h3>\n                        <p><strong>Breed:</strong> Holland Lop</p>\n                        <p><strong>Age:</strong> 1 year</p>\n                        <p><strong>Gender:</strong> Male</p>\n                        <p>Rocky is an energetic and charming rabbit who loves to explore. He enjoys fresh greens and a good chew toy.</p>\n                        <a href=\"#\" class=\"cta-button\">Learn More & Adopt</a>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"animal-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/250x200/cccccc/ffffff?text=Daisy+the+Dog\" alt=\"Daisy the Dog\">\n                    <div class=\"animal-info\">\n                        <h3>Daisy</h3>\n                        <p><strong>Breed:</strong> Beagle</p>\n                        <p><strong>Age:</strong> 5 years</p>\n                        <p><strong>Gender:</strong> Female</p>\n                        <p>Daisy is a loyal and gentle companion looking for a quiet home. She enjoys gentle walks and lots of ear scratches.</p>\n                        <a href=\"#\" class=\"cta-button\">Learn More & Adopt</a>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div style=\"text-align: center; margin-top: 30px;\">\n                <a href=\"#\" class=\"cta-button\">View All Adoptable Animals</a>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n        <section id=\"volunteer\">\n            <h2>Help Us Make a Difference</h2>\n            <p>Volunteers are the heart of our shelter! Whether it's walking dogs, socializing cats, helping with events, or assisting with administrative tasks, your time and effort are invaluable. Join our team and experience the joy of helping animals in need.</p>\n            <a href=\"#\" class=\"cta-button\">Become a Volunteer</a>\n        </section>\n        <section id=\"donate\">\n            <h2>Support Our Mission</h2>\n            <p>Your donations help us provide food, shelter, medical care, and enrichment for all our animals. Every contribution, big or small, makes a significant impact on their lives. You can donate online, by mail, or in person.</p>\n            <a href=\"#\" class=\"cta-button\">Donate Today</a>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Pawsitive Connections Animal Shelter. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n</body>\n</html>"}